              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="b4b7-5338-e8e2-41fd">Attached model loses Cloudwalk and cannot gain it.
In the End Phase, your opponent makes a Ranged Attack against the Attached model with the following Ranged Weapon: Call Lightning (-1).
The Ranged Pool is equal to the turn number. The range is always medium. 
his attack ignores models in BtB, Cover and Ranged Defence.


Requirement [Sojobo]</characteristic>
              </characteristics>
            </profile>
          </profiles>
          <categoryLinks>
