            <profile name="Equestrian Leg Yield" typeId="d2bb-86b4-edf3-c4e5" typeName="Special Card" hidden="false" id="b5c4-aafe-33fa-3c45">
              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="b4b7-5338-e8e2-41fd">During an Enemy model&apos;s activation in which it entered into BtB with, or Targets, the Attached Friendly Samurai model with a Ranged Attack or Ki Feat, but before any Melee Exchange begins; make an Opposed Move Test.
If successful, place the Attached model within 2&quot; of its current location, the Enemy model&apos;s action is then considered resolved. Discard this Card.
This is a Trap Effect.

Requirement [Samurai]</characteristic>
              </characteristics>
            </profile>
          </profiles>
          <modifiers>
