        <profile name="Hit &amp; Run" typeId="d2bb-86b4-edf3-c4e5" typeName="Special Card" hidden="false" id="a861-f8fb-3dc4-9842">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="b4b7-5338-e8e2-41fd">- When a Charge Attack Damage Roll Kills an Enemy model, the Charging Samurai may make a Walk equal to its Move Statistic.
- Once per game use this ability in the Starting Phase, until the End Phase Friendly models may use their Cavalry Trait before AND after their Action.
- The first time, each turn, a Friendly model is successful on a Charge Attack Roll, that model suffers half Damage on any Damage Roll from the same Melee Exchange.
- You must recruit a Curse card into the Warband.

Permitted [Samurai]</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <modifiers>
        <modifier type="set" value="true" field="hidden">
          <conditionGroups>
            <conditionGroup type="and">
              <conditions>
